{"tid":975880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免簽地區數目　港護照排名跌","createTime":"2019-01-10T04:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T13:26:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf5d688a21801bd8467e98b2cdf3e7dd930703a","tid":975880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190110/20587892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F20587892&d=XYjAR2kfDNRlBgPoxB6BaNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4e609f7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F20587892&h=e6d55746\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190110/20587892</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月10日 <br />\n<br />\n免簽地區數目　港護照排名跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190110/large/a0804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190110%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.jpg&h=be382a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際移民公司恆理環球顧問事務所（Henley &amp; Partners）公佈2019年度最新的「亨氏護照指數」（Henley Passport Index），日本護照憑着190個地區免簽證待遇連續兩年膺選「地上最強護照」，並列第2的新加坡及南韓護照，免簽地區數量跟日本只差1個；法國及德國護照則以188地區免簽一起屈居第3；香港特區護照擁169個免簽地區，數目較去年減少1個，排名比去年下滑兩位至第19。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的護照免簽地區數量比去年增加一個，至149個國家，排名維持在第29名；澳門特區護照排32位；中國大陸護照仍和去年一樣擁有74個免簽地區，但排名從去年的第71位上升至第69名。歐洲國家的護照表現普遍不俗，丹麥、芬蘭、意大利、瑞典以187免簽地區並列第4；盧森堡和西班牙排名第5，擁有186個免簽地區。至於4年前並稱全球最方便的美國及英國護照，排名持續下滑，今年以185個免簽地區數量，跟奧地利、荷蘭、挪威、葡萄牙、瑞士同列第6位。<br />\n<br />\n至於全球「最不受歡迎」的護照仍然是阿富汗和伊拉克，僅獲30地區免簽，在排行榜上敬陪末座。<br />\n<br />\n恆理環球顧問事務所網站  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n外牆唧膠失足　裝修工26樓墮下亡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n醫委會拒訂醫生執業年齡上限"},{"pid":"0dc222b7078cb8a721dca1e62aa45e2527fac3cf","tid":975880,"uid":41423,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"取消歐盟/日/韓免簽,港豬就會反抗"},{"pid":"7544a2f86155463dbb457d8149daec5e247d25bc","tid":975880,"uid":128761,"like":50,"dislike":3,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"香港如果唔係中國<br />\n變到頭三甲甚至超越日本都冇問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw日本人係少數免簽去中國既人<br />\n但你地知唔知中國人普遍相信一個講法係<br />\n中國政府為左比香港人免簽去日本，而甘願比日本人免簽去中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db90d6ce5cf7529bbd5bca2232ade3e4ab264e41","tid":975880,"uid":62350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"邊一個冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6245f3e732da8f483840230c1b85805c2489916f","tid":975880,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"減少咗邊個？"},{"pid":"b89ee31e274753cd33d02452c6a226893679d04d","tid":975880,"uid":82640,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:24:24.000Z","msg":"好心入境處出返通知話俾香港人邊個國家取消咗香港免簽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b956e85a21ddeb90b69213e5f7952ea46615ba91","tid":975880,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b89ee31e274753cd33d02452c6a226893679d04d","tid":975880,"uid":82640,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:24:24.000Z","msg":"好心入境處出返通知話俾香港人邊個國家取消咗香港免簽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌，港特"},{"pid":"7a463a103be79d9bc770243632fe5056ac6d5f0f","tid":975880,"uid":207247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7544a2f86155463dbb457d8149daec5e247d25bc","tid":975880,"uid":128761,"like":50,"dislike":3,"score":47,"cite